---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Kalyan AI" description="Privacy Policy for Kalyan AI">
	<section class="ka-card p-8 my-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="text-[var(--muted)] mb-4">Last updated: February 2026</p>

		<div class="prose text-[var(--muted)] space-y-4">
			<p>Kalyan AI ("we", "us", or "our") is a sole trader business based in Birmingham, UK. This policy explains how we handle your personal data.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mt-6 mb-3">What we collect</h2>
			<p>When you book a call or contact us, we collect:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
				<li>Name and email address</li>
				<li>Company name (if provided)</li>
				<li>Information you share about your business needs</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mt-6 mb-3">How we use it</h2>
			<p>We use your information to:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
				<li>Respond to enquiries and schedule calls</li>
				<li>Deliver our services if you become a client</li>
				<li>Send relevant updates (only with your consent)</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mt-6 mb-3">Third parties</h2>
			<p>We use Calendly for scheduling. When you book a call, Calendly processes your data under their own privacy policy. We do not sell or share your data with anyone else.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mt-6 mb-3">Your rights</h2>
			<p>Under UK GDPR, you can request access to, correction of, or deletion of your data. Contact us at future@kalyanai.io.</p>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mt-6 mb-3">Contact</h2>
			<p>Kalyan AI<br />Bradford Business Court, 121â€“123 Bradford Street, Birmingham, B12 0NS<br />future@kalyanai.io</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
